    "caption": "Since it’s the month of love, we want to shoutout the ones we love most! @lindsay_mataya this one’s for you!\n\n“Becoming close with Lindsay sophomore year through living in the house right next to eachother has been one of my biggest blessings in college. We spent every moment together pushing each-other, leaning on one another and loving each other like real sisters. Lindsay convinced me to travel to Portugal with her for one month and I’m so happy she did. She pulled me out of my shell and I got to travel the world with my best friend. The experiences and memories we made I will forever cherish. She is my ride or die and I wouldn’t change our friendship for the world.”\nLove you linds, love lizard 🩵",
