    "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DUWJpbAEZOs/",
    "caption": "Bria (PC 25)! From Alpharetta, GA! Here’s what she has to say about being in AOII!\n\n“Going into rush, I kept a completely open mind and truly wanted to pick the chapter that felt most at home to me. I knew Shay loved AOII but wanted to make my own decision without any influence from anyone else. However, when I walked into AOII I knew it was home. There was an immediate sense of warmth and excitement and I knew that it was meant to be. Not only did I gain so many new friends, but I grew even closer to my sister. Being in the same chapter as my sister has made this place feel even more at home, and I am forever grateful for AOII!“ - Bria Blount \n\nWe love you!! 🩵🩵🩵",
